{"tid":1015963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手遊結識12歲男童　22歲嫩媽邀共赴巫山被捕","createTime":"2019-02-10T13:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T15:23:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c316cdc0d1cfeef5a6dba06d9e01e1432403ecb5","tid":1015963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190125/photo/bkn-20190125060048138-0125_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190125163843\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190125060048138-0125_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190125163843&h=776f0c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本一名22歲年輕女子早前玩手機網絡遊戲時，認識了一名年僅12歲的男童，她更邀請對方前來家中上床，女子事後被捕。案件曝光後有網民對她「起底」，發現她不僅長相甜美，而且是一名單親母親。<br />\n<br />\n住在香川縣高松市的售貨員長尾里佳，早前透過手機遊戲認識涉案小學生，二人周一（21日）中午在女方家中發生性行為。警方接到匿名人士報案後，翌日拘捕長尾里佳。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，長尾里佳被盤問時，將事件經過和盤托出，現時被控強制性交等多項罪名。案件曝光後，有網民展開「人肉搜尋」，發覺她不僅長相甜美，而且育有一名年約4歲的女兒。網民對她自毀前程，紛紛感到難以置信。"},{"pid":"edad34a52942e4a51ea4aece24abef91eed81a74","tid":1015963,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9560d6b15a1c63fc4c56308bcef4b056c5bf4d4c","tid":1015963,"uid":142067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"好過份..無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecbdbb9161f74f9d9f3b2095339acbdcb6dffd7","tid":1015963,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"當我有講過"},{"pid":"60315c0d0e783f204abeab495658e46524caa292","tid":1015963,"uid":216519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快</span></span>"},{"pid":"736066d58ac2